)\n\n| Service | Image | Port |\n|---------|-------|------|\n| **web** | Custom build (FastAPI app) | 11000 |\n| **postgres** | `postgres` | 5432 |\n| **redis** | `redis:alpine` | 6379 |\n\nThe app targets **Python 3.9** and uses **Pipfile/Pipenv** for dependency management.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 574, "prompt_tokens": 11450, "total_tokens": 12024, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 17, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 10304, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.0010349844, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 0.0005356044, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.00049938}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-pro-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780962709-fKDSCYWNBn78ZwNUMK1T", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea9a6-4f6e-76e0-959f-c6cbcfc6618f-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 11450, "output_tokens": 574, "total_tokens": 12024, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 10304}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 17}}}}]}}}
